{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2343461, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另一位洞友的每晚问题 #448349", "timestamp": 1629739901, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2344052, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "tips: [0, m] 中第一个被输出的数在 [0, m] 中等可能随机", "timestamp": 1629769442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2346357, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "由于输出的数单调不增，所以「x 被输出至少一次」等价于「[0, x] 中第一个被输出的数是 x」，由楼上 tips 可知这个概率为 1 / (x + 1)。三个事件互相独立，因此 p = 1 / (999 + 1)(99 + 1)(9 + 1) = 10^-6。", "timestamp": 1629793322, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2346364, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": 2343461, "tag": null, "text": "希望 dz 把这个系列继续下去！", "timestamp": 1629793458, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2348456, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": 2346357, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: Alice 正解！🦊\n我继续加油嗷", "timestamp": 1629817135, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2352028, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 713, "w": 668}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "严格地用了一下递推", "timestamp": 1629872121, "type": "image", "url": "6a/6athkv7slw6fsbhgamjvm6eimq4vxsjl.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2352052, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 825, "w": 595}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还有变种的问题", "timestamp": 1629872379, "type": "image", "url": "lv/lvhi3orq5nympv2xfvyrytmmesawjgcu.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2369772, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 448466, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 这题妙耶！", "timestamp": 1630074613, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 448466, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "#每晚问题 5\n上期 #446973\n设 a < b 是整数，用 rnd(a, b) 表示在 a, a+1, ..., b 中等可能地随机选择的一个整数。\n今执行下述程序：\n\n1. n = 2021\n2. n = rnd(0, n)\n3. 输出 n\n4. 如果 n > 0，则回到 2. ；否则结束。\n\n记“执行过程中，999、99、9这三个数全都被输出了至少一次”的概率是 p。则 p 的常用对数（即 10 为底对数）最接近\n", "timestamp": 1629739558, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630074612, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"-8": 10, "-6": 18, "-4": 3, "-2": 3}, "vote_options": ["-8", "-6", "-4", "-2"]}}}